            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>Reference:HSK Standard Course 2</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p><span class="plainlinks"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://amzn.to/2rvrOQs"><img width="300" class="alignright link-amazon" src="https&#58;//images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/41hFHgzVCFL._SX368_BO1,204,203,200_.jpg" /></a></span>
<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://amzn.to/2rvrOQs">HSK Standard Course 2</a>, by Liu Chang and Lu Jiang, contains 15 lessons. Authorized by Hanban, HSK Standard Course is developed under the joint efforts of Beijing Language and Culture University Press and Chinese Testing International (CTI). With HSK test papers as its primary source, HSK Standard Course is characterized by a humorous style, familiar topics and a scientific course design.
</p><p>You may also want to refer to our full list of <a href="HSK_2_grammar_points" title="HSK 2 grammar points">HSK 2 grammar points</a>.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="./Reference:HSK_Standard_Course_2#Grammar_Points_by_Table_of_Contents"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Grammar Points by Table of Contents</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="./Reference:HSK_Standard_Course_2#Grammar_Point_References_to_This_Book"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Grammar Point References to This Book</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="./Reference:HSK_Standard_Course_2#HSK_Standard_Course_.28HSK_.E6.A0.87.E5.87.86.E6.95.99.E7.A8.8B.29"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">HSK Standard Course (HSK 标准教程)</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="./Reference:HSK_Standard_Course_2#See_also"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">See also</span></a></li>
