<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Grammar_Points_by_Table_of_Contents">Grammar Points by Table of Contents</span></h2>
<ol><li>Lesson 1: 九月去北京旅游最好 September is the best time to visit Beijing
<ol><li><a href="Wanting_to_do_something_with_&quot;yao&quot;" title="Wanting to do something with &quot;yao&quot;">助动词“要” The Auxiliary Verb "要"</a></li>
<li><a href="Superlative_&quot;zui&quot;" title="Superlative &quot;zui&quot;">程度副词：最 The Adverb of Degree "最" </a></li>
<li><a href="Using_&quot;ji&quot;_to_mean_&quot;several&quot;" title="Using &quot;ji&quot; to mean &quot;several&quot;">概数的表达：几、多"几" and "多": expressions of approximate numbers </a>  (see also <a href="Indicating_a_number_in_excess" title="Indicating a number in excess">Indicating a number in excess</a>)</li></ol></li>
<li>Lesson 2: 我每天六点起床 I get up at six every day
<ol><li><a href="Affirmative-negative_question" title="Affirmative-negative question">用“是不是” 的问句 Questions Using "是不是"</a> (see also <a href="Tag_questions_with_&quot;bu&quot;" title="Tag questions with &quot;bu&quot;">Tag questions with "bu"</a>)</li>
<li><a href="Expressing_&quot;every&quot;_with_&quot;mei&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;every&quot; with &quot;mei&quot;">代词“每” The Pronoun"每" </a></li>
<li><a href="Asking_about_degree_with_&quot;duo&quot;" title="Asking about degree with &quot;duo&quot;">疑问代词“多” The Interrogative Pronoun"多"</a></li></ol></li>
<li>Lesson 3: 左边那个红色的是我的 The red one on the left is mine
<ol><li><a href="Modifying_nouns_with_phrase_+_&quot;de&quot;" title="Modifying nouns with phrase + &quot;de&quot;">“的” 字短语The "的" Phrase</a></li>
<li><a href="Verbing_briefly_with_&quot;yixia&quot;" title="Verbing briefly with &quot;yixia&quot;">一下 The Numeral Classifier "一下"</a></li>
<li><a href="Expressing_&quot;really&quot;_with_&quot;zhen&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;really&quot; with &quot;zhen&quot;">语气副词“真” The Modal Adverb "真"</a></li></ol></li>
<li>Lesson 4: 这个工作是他帮我介绍的 He recommended me for this job
<ol><li><a href="The_&quot;shi..._de&quot;_construction_for_indicating_purpose" title="The &quot;shi... de&quot; construction for indicating purpose">“是……的” 句：强调施事 The Structure "是……的": emphasizing the agent of an action</a></li>
<li><a href="Expressing_&quot;when&quot;_with_&quot;de_shihou&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;when&quot; with &quot;de shihou&quot;">表示时间：……的时候"……的时候" Indicating Time</a></li>
<li><a href="Expressing_&quot;already&quot;_with_&quot;yijing&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;already&quot; with &quot;yijing&quot;">时间副词“已经” The Adverb of Time "已经"</a></li></ol></li>
<li>Lesson 5: 就买这件吧 Take this one
<ol><li><a href="Expressing_&quot;then&quot;_with_&quot;jiu&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;then&quot; with &quot;jiu&quot;">副词“就” The Adverb "就"</a></li>
<li><a href="Moderating_positive_adjectives_with_&quot;hai&quot;" title="Moderating positive adjectives with &quot;hai&quot;">语气副词“还”（1）The Modal Adverb "还"(1)</a></li>
<li><a href="Expressing_&quot;a_little_too&quot;_with_&quot;you_dian&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;a little too&quot; with &quot;you dian&quot;">程度副词“有点儿” The Adverbial Modifier "有点儿"</a></li></ol></li>
<li>Lesson 6: 你怎么不吃了 Why don't you eat more
<ol><li><a href="Asking_why_with_&quot;zenme&quot;" title="Asking why with &quot;zenme&quot;">疑问代词“怎么” The Interrogative Pronoun "怎么"</a></li>
<li><a href="Reduplication_of_measure_words" title="Reduplication of measure words">量词的重叠 Reduplication of Measure Words</a></li>
<li><a href="Cause_and_effect_with_&quot;yinwei&quot;_and_&quot;suoyi&quot;" title="Cause and effect with &quot;yinwei&quot; and &quot;suoyi&quot;">关联词“因为……，所以……” The Pair of Conjunctions "因为……，所以……" </a></li></ol></li>
<li>Lesson 7: 你家离公司远吗 Do you live far from your company
<ol><li><a href="Continuation_with_&quot;hai&quot;" title="Continuation with &quot;hai&quot;">语气副词“还”（2）The Modal Adverb "还"(2)</a></li>
<li><a href="Expressing_earliness_with_&quot;jiu&quot;" title="Expressing earliness with &quot;jiu&quot;">时间副词“就” The Adverb of Time "就"</a></li>
<li><a href="Expressing_distance_with_&quot;li&quot;" title="Expressing distance with &quot;li&quot;">离 The Verb "离"</a></li>
<li><a href="Modal_particle_&quot;ne&quot;" title="Modal particle &quot;ne&quot;">语气助词“呢” The Modal Particle "呢"</a></li></ol></li>
<li>Lesson 8: 让我想想再告诉你 Let me think about it and I'll tell you later
<ol><li><a href="Tag_questions_with_&quot;ma&quot;" title="Tag questions with &quot;ma&quot;">疑问句“……，好吗” The Interrogative Sentence "……，好吗"</a></li>
<li><a href="Expressing_&quot;again&quot;_in_the_future_with_&quot;zai&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;again&quot; in the future with &quot;zai&quot;">副词“再” The Adverb "再"</a></li>
<li><a href="Causative_verbs" title="Causative verbs">兼语句 Pivotal Sentences</a></li>
<li><a href="Reduplication_of_verbs" title="Reduplication of verbs">动词的重叠 Reduplication of Verbs</a></li></ol></li>
<li>Lesson 9:
